 \"a world\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"30.69 seconds\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the unofficial 300m distance\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 869}, {\"ngram\": \"the Backtrack Classic Shootout\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"a 400m\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"the ASA Grand Prix\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital city\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday night\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though he clearly pushed hard, and took some time to recover on the side of the track before he could conduct interviews, Tebogo insisted he could have gone quicker at the Grand Prix meeting after easing up before the finish line.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"the side\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"interviews\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"the Grand Prix meeting\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't tired.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is more than what I did today.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just that we do not want to bring it up this early in the season,\\\" he said after the second 400m race of his senior career.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"the second 400m race\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"his senior career\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Viva Botswana \\ud83e\\udd0c\\ud83e\\udd0c@tebogo_letsilePowers to a 44:29 World Lead to win the men's 400m Tuks Grandprix#ContinentalTour#GrandPrixpic.twitter.com/lcjJ2CQogK Tebogo confirmed he would return to shorter distances for the rest of the year, with his sights set on Olympic glory.\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/400_metres\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.541410808697177e-26, \"text\": \"400m\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/400_metres\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/400_metres\"}, {\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Pretoria\", \"score\": 0.9999999998822204, \"rank\": 1.1693509920908826e-10, \"text\": \"Tuks\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Pretoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Pretoria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Botswana\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"a 44:29 World Lead\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"lcjJ2CQogK Tebogo\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"shorter distances\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"his sights\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic glory\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will go back to the drawing board and analyse the video, but I think this will be my last 400m race until further notice,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the drawing board\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"my last 400m race\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"further notice\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For now we will rest a bit and get the body back to 